name: Cubedesktop
tag_list: software, desktop, windows, vista, computer, virtual, 3d, Visualization
overview:
CubeDesktop is a new (March 2008) 3D virtual desktop environment for Windows that will change the way you work. CubeDesktop helps you to reduce clutter and better organize your windowed applications by providing up to six virtual desktops which you can manage using innovative 2D and 3D effects.

On Feb 1 2008 - Thinking Minds Building Bytes, a privately owned Spanish company, acquire all development and distribution rights of CubeDesktop.u5ur
